'''潔姬·克魯茲'''（{{lang-en|Jackie Cruz}}，{{bd|1986年|8月8日}}）<ref name="six"/><ref name="official_t"/><ref name="official_t2"/>是一名[[多明尼加共和國|多明尼加]]裔[[美國|美國]]<ref name="thr">{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/orange-is-new-blacks-latinas-658905|title='Orange Is the New Black's' Latinas – The Hollywood Reporter|work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=[[Prometheus_Global_Media|Prometheus Global Media]]|date=2013-11-22|access-date=2015-06-17|archive-date=2018-07-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180705092924/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/lists/orange-is-new-blacks-latinas-658905|dead-url=yes}}</ref>女演員、歌手和前模特兒。她以其在[[Netflix|Netflix]]原創劇集《[[勁爆女子監獄|勁爆女子監獄]]》（2013年至2019年）中飾演瑪莉索·「夫拉卡」·岡薩雷斯（{{lang|en|Marisol "Flaca" Gonzales}}）而聞名。2020年起在[[全國廣播公司|NBC]]《[[乖乖女|乖乖女]]》常駐演出。

== 早期生活 ==
潔姬·克魯茲以賈桂琳·查維茲（{{lang|en|Jacqueline Chavez}}）一名出生於[[紐約市|紐約市]][[皇后區|皇后區]]，在美國[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]和[[多明尼加共和國|多明尼加共和國]][[聖地牙哥_(多明尼加)|聖地牙哥]]之間成長<ref name="remezcla">{{cite web|url=http://remezcla.com/features/jackie-cruz-of-orange-is-the-new-black-on-songwriting-surviving-a-car-crash-hollywood-stereotypes-film|title=Jackie Cruz of 'Orange is the New Black' on Songwriting and Surviving a Crash {{!}} Film {{!}} Remezcla|work=Remezcla|last=Erazo|first=Vanessa|date=2014-06-24|access-date=2015-06-20|archive-date=2015-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150919082206/http://remezcla.com/features/jackie-cruz-of-orange-is-the-new-black-on-songwriting-surviving-a-car-crash-hollywood-stereotypes-film/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她由單身母親撫養長大，她本身講有一口流利的英語和西班牙語<ref name="latintimes2">{{cite web|url=http://www.latintimes.com/oitnb-actress-jackie-cruz-opens-about-diversity-dating-hollywood-and-her-character-323552|title='OITNB' Actress Jackie Cruz Opens Up About Diversity, Dating in Hollywood And Her Character 'Flaca' [PHOTOS]|work=Latin Times|publisher=IBT Media|last=Roterman|first=Natalie|date=2015-06-18|access-date=2015-06-20|archive-date=2018-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180806154759/https://www.latintimes.com/oitnb-actress-jackie-cruz-opens-about-diversity-dating-hollywood-and-her-character-323552|dead-url=no}}</ref>。克魯茲在7歲時受《[[終極保鑣|終極保鑣]]》（1992年）的[[惠妮·休斯頓|惠妮·休斯頓]]啟發而決定成為藝人<ref name="latintimes"/>。她在洛杉磯的{{le|亞歷山大·漢密爾頓高中 (洛杉磯)|Alexander Hamilton High School (Los Angeles)|亞歷山大·漢密爾頓高中}}，當時她是該學校音樂學院的成員。<ref name="latintimes">{{cite web|work=[[Latin_Times|Latin Times]]|title=Latinos In The US: Jackie Cruz, 'Orange Is The New Black' Star, On Her Background, Work In NYC And Being Latina|date=2013-10-24|author=Valdez, Maria G.|url=https://www.latintimes.com/latinos-us-jackie-cruz-orange-new-blac|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180702180441/https://www.latintimes.com/latinos-us-jackie-cruz-orange-new-black-star-her-background-work-nyc-and-being-latina-132271|archive-date=2018-07-02|publisher=Newsweek Media Group}}</ref>

克魯茲16歲那年，搬出了母親的公寓，成了無家可歸的人<ref name="remezcla"/>。17歲時，她是一場車禍的受害者，造成[[氣胸|氣胸]]並陷入昏迷，需要進行腦部手術<ref name="official">{{cite web|url=http://www.jackiecruz.com/bio.html|title=Jackie Cruz American Singer and Songwriter Bio|work=JackieCruz.com|access-date=2015-06-19|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304225946/http://www.jackiecruz.com/bio.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="latintimes"/>。她的歌曲〈甜蜜的十六歲〉（{{lang|en|Sweet Sixteen}}）取材自該事件。<ref name="remezcla"/>

== 個人生活 ==
克魯茲是[[雙性戀|雙性戀]]。2016年，克魯茲告訴{{le|AfterEllen|AfterEllen}}網站：「我喜歡這個人是否是女人－我們不喜歡被貼上標籤。我現在和男人有戀愛關係，但是我過去很喜歡女人。所以我猜想我們不想被貼上標籤，我們並沒有真正談論它，但是這些行動勝於雄辯，是嗎？所以，你看到了它，你這樣活。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.afterellen.com/celebs/471441-jackie-cruz-bisexuality-orange-new-black-friendship-ruby-rose|title=Jackie Cruz on bisexuality on "Orange is the New Black" and her friendship with Ruby Rose - AfterEllen|date=2016-01-27|access-date=2021-03-08|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918083822/https://afterellen.com/celebs/471441-jackie-cruz-bisexuality-orange-new-black-friendship-ruby-rose|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pride.com/women/2016/7/21/these-9-rad-queer-women-color-prove-representation-matters#slide-5|title=These 9 Rad Queer Women of Color Prove Representation Matters|date=2016-07-21|access-date=2021-03-08|archive-date=2016-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161030020943/http://www.pride.com/women/2016/7/21/these-9-rad-queer-women-color-prove-representation-matters#slide-5|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年8月，克魯茲與藝術家費爾南多·賈西亞（{{lang|en|Fernando Garcia}}）結婚<ref>{{Cite news|date=2020-08-30|title='Orange Is the New Black' Star Jackie Cruz Marries Fernando Garcia|work=[[Entertainment_Tonight|Entertainment Tonight]]}}</ref>。

